stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initial
    Initial --> ScalingUp : Data growth detected
    ScalingUp --> StorageOptimized : Storage optimization applied
    ScalingUp --> IndexingOptimized : Indexing optimization applied
    StorageOptimized --> Stable : Performance stable
    IndexingOptimized --> Stable : Performance stable
    Stable --> ScalingDown : Data growth decreases
    ScalingDown --> [*] : System returns to normal